    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(center)">
                <placeName>Baltimore</placeName>
                <date>Octr 18<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1835</date>
            </p>
            <p>Dear <addressee>Isaac</addressee></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I recd your letter by <persName>Mr Mordecai</persName> with the
                    <sic>almanak</sic><lb/> for which I thank you I should have send for one but
                    <persName>Miss Etting</persName><lb/> loaned me one which she had to spare
                    <persName>Mr Mor</persName> called at my House<lb/> last <add>Hebrew</add>
                <add>?</add> but I was from home I met him in the street, near <persName>Mr
                    Cohens</persName><add>?</add><lb/> had but little chance to talk to him
                    <persName>Mr Levy</persName> who will hand you<lb/> this called at my house, he
                says he does not know the reason why<lb/> you have not called at his house for a
                long time past tho he was<lb/>
                <sic>agains</sic> you getting $1000 yet he says he is as great a friend of
                yours<lb/> any in the city others of your congregation also find fault with you<lb/>
                not calling to see them <persName>Mr Philips</persName> for one who is one of
                the<lb/> pinto<add>?</add> says you <sic>was</sic> not at his house since the
                    <sic>marige</sic> of his daughter<lb/> the <sic>coustom</sic> is in every part
                were I have been for <add>Hebrew</add> to call<lb/>
                <sic>occationly</sic> to see them particularly on <add>Hebrew</add>. I do not
                know<lb/> what to say to you your own <sic>sence</sic> will tell you that if<lb/>
                one <sic>freind</sic> is gained is worth a little sacrifice of feeling<lb/> we are
                all well and all wish you well and <sic>genarly</sic> partake<lb/> what is for your
                good and feel hurt at any thing what is<lb/> against your <sic>intress</sic> or
                feeling I remain your <sic>freind</sic></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <persName role="author">Zalma Rehine</persName>
            </p>
            <p>Your Aunt <persName>Mrs Depass</persName>
                <persName>D</persName>
                <persName>Judah</persName>
                <persName>Abby</persName> and all your friends<lb/> send <sic>they</sic> Love to you
                and to <persName>Mr &amp; Mrs Peixottos</persName> familia<lb/> let me hear from you
                soon</p>
            <pb n="4"/>
            <p>
                <addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p>per favour of <persName>Mr Levy</persName></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
        </body>
